= Legal & Compliance =

(% class="box infomessage" %)
(((
**TL;DR: Our Rules**
🎯 **Goal**: Ensure independence, transparency, and user protection.
⚖️ **Core Rule**: No single donor can provide more than 20% of our annual budget (Editorial Firewall).
📜 **Open Source**: Code is licensed under **AGPL-3.0** / **MIT**; data is **CC BY-SA 4.0**.
)))

